org.codethechange.culturemesh.models

Class Country

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.codethechange.culturemesh.models.Location
      • org.codethechange.culturemesh.models.Place
        • org.codethechange.culturemesh.models.Country
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, Listable

    public class Country
extends Place
    A Country is a specific kind of Place that stores the ID and name of a country. No instance field should ever be set to Place.NOWHERE.
    See Also:
